title: Miami Heat Forward Chris Bosh joins Levi Maestro - 'The Maestro'
text:
CONNECT ABOUT THE MAESTRO 
Los Angeles-based film maker/personality Levi Maestro is creating a new online series for FOX Sports entitled "The Maestro." This series is an adapted format of Levi's current series "Maestro Knows," which began in 2009 and features short-form pieces that entertain and educate audiences about guests of all different creative efforts. In "The Maestro," figures from the world of sports take center stage. CONNECT WITH THE MAESTRO
